snippet.title: Good N Dead - Official Trailer for Steam Game Festival: Autumn Edition
snippet.description:
Coming to PC, Mac, and Linux in 2020!
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/13...

https://goodndead.com/

📢 Subscribe to our mailing list: https://grimthinking.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/CcGP4ex
🐤 Twitter: https://twitter.com/GrimThinkingLLC

Good N Dead is a zombie survival couch co-op tower defense game for 1-4 players.

Music by AShamaluevMusic.
Website: https://www.ashamaluevmusic.com
